      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LESTER RHODE (1) was checked in the run and safely held when sixth (20.07) in a Restricted WIN over 340m at this track. Better than latest and worth another try. MYSTIC GAZE (4) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth at this track, but was among the placings at Launceston three back. Can hit the frame this time. BLACKBRUSH CADET (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 340m behind Grapefruit Racer (20.11) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings seven times from 14 starts. Cannot be taken lightly. TIMELESS GRACIE (3) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
